						<summary>

						<p>Slab [2] set up in the mūḍabasti of Vardhamānasvāmi temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">1510 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This very much damaged record speaks of a land grant made by Rāmusāla to the various services in the basati of Vardhamānasvāmi.</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka 1433, Pramōda, Vaiśākha, Śu. 10, Thursday corresponding to 1510 A.D., April 18, Thursday.</p>						

						</summary>
